thread.title: KAYE
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by KAYE

author: KAYE
title: KAYE
text:
Wonderful helpful service from Staff, Firstly had 2 door Kia - new and lovely but too small. Dave and Emma? said to call next day and they would save a bigger car for us which they did. We had a Kia Cerato which
was great for the 11 days stay. Also gave us a Road Directory.
Could not speak highly enough of the staff at Hobart Redspot office. Big smiles and ready to help.
